parse.title: List of towns and cities with 100,000 or more inhabitants/country: P-Q-R-S

text.*:
This is a list of towns and cities in the world in alphabetical order, beginning with the letters P, Q, R and S, by country believed to have 100,000 or more inhabitants. Unless otherwise noted, populations are based on 2006 United Nations estimates.
